# 3d Lennard
label tloop

variable T index 0.5 2.5 # Solid, liquid

units lj
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic

lattice fcc 1.5
region simbox block 0 10 0 10 0 10
create_box 1 simbox
create_atoms 1 box

mass 1 1.0

velocity all create ${T} 87287 dist uniform

pair_style lj/cut 3.0
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0 3.0

compute myMSD all msd

fix 1 all nve

dump 1 all custom 100 dump.radial_dist_T${T} id type x y z vx vy vz
thermo 100

thermo_style custom step temp press c_myMSD[4]

run 200000

clear
next T
jump SELF tloop
